WEBVTT

00:00:04.022 --> 00:00:05.291
<i>(water droplets dripping)</i>

00:00:09.751 --> 00:00:11.751
<i>(hollow icy ambience)</i>

00:00:14.763 --> 00:00:17.099
<v Proog>Proog: (stuttering) <i>At the left we can see—</i></v>

00:00:17.124 --> 00:00:18.240
<v Proog><i>but we can see the—</i></v>

00:00:18.560 --> 00:00:20.490
<v Proog><i>at the right we can see the…</i></v>

00:00:20.515 --> 00:00:21.777
<v Proog><i>… the head‐snarlers.</i></v>

00:00:21.802 --> 00:00:24.495
<v Proog>And everything is safe… perfectly safe.

00:00:24.521 --> 00:00:26.052
<v Proog>(gasps) Emo?</v>

00:00:26.077 --> 00:00:27.242
<v Proog>Emo!</v>
♪ (suspenseful music)

00:00:27.267 --> 00:00:28.797
<i>(high‐pitched feedback squeal)</i>

00:00:28.822 --> 00:00:30.822
<v Proog>Proog: Watch out!</v>
<v Emo>Emo: (knocked over) Ow!</v>

00:00:31.146 --> 00:00:32.378
<i>(electric zaps, cables clank)</i>

00:00:32.414 --> 00:00:34.125
<i>(high‐pitched feedback squeal)</i>

00:00:34.150 --> 00:00:35.150
<i>(electric sparks)</i>

00:00:36.497 --> 00:00:38.497
<i>(quiet, indistinct chattering)</i>

00:00:46.830 --> 00:00:47.838
<v Proog>Proog: Are you hurt?</v>

00:00:47.871 --> 00:00:50.414
<i>(wind blows)</i>

00:00:52.086 --> 00:00:54.037
<v Emo>Emo: I don’t think so. You?</v>

00:00:55.682 --> 00:00:56.721
<v Proog>Proog: I’m okay.</v>

00:00:57.631 --> 00:01:01.083
<v Proog>Get up! Emo, it’s not safe here.</v>

00:01:01.966 --> 00:01:03.146
<v Proog>Let’s go.</v>

00:01:03.591 --> 00:01:04.591
<v Emo>Emo: What’s next?</v>

00:01:05.577 --> 00:01:06.906
<v Proog>Proog: You’ll see!</v>

00:01:07.687 --> 00:01:08.960
<v Emo>Emo: You’ll see…</v>

00:01:09.753 --> 00:01:11.753
<i>(cold wind blowing softly)</i>

00:01:15.994 --> 00:01:18.021
<v Proog>Proog: Emo, this way.</v>

00:01:23.807 --> 00:01:27.940
♪ (eerie high‐pitched notes)

00:01:27.965 --> 00:01:28.965
<i>(electric sparks)</i>

00:01:29.693 --> 00:01:31.347
<i>(footsteps get louder)</i>

00:01:31.372 --> 00:01:32.446
<i>(electric sparks)</i>

00:01:32.471 --> 00:01:34.536
<i>(ominous crackling static)</i>

00:01:34.561 --> 00:01:35.605
<v Proog>Proog: Follow me!</v>

00:01:35.630 --> 00:01:37.644
<i>(resonant bell chimes)</i>

00:01:38.236 --> 00:01:40.203
♪ (fast‐paced intense music)

00:01:41.218 --> 00:01:42.781
<i>(electric sparks)</i>

00:01:42.806 --> 00:01:45.473
<i>(rapid wing flapping)</i>

00:01:50.557 --> 00:01:51.557
♪ (music intensifies)

00:01:53.903 --> 00:01:55.458
<i>(wings flap, bird panting)</i>

00:02:11.245 --> 00:02:12.245
<v Proog>Proog: Hurry, Emo!</v>

00:02:14.698 --> 00:02:16.147
♪ (music reaches peak intensity)

00:02:17.043 --> 00:02:20.303
<i>(chattering in foreign language)</i>

00:02:23.087 --> 00:02:24.678
<i>(birds chirping erratically)</i>

00:02:24.703 --> 00:02:26.049
<i>(wings flapping)</i>

00:02:26.309 --> 00:02:28.568
<i>(robotic gurgling)</i>

00:02:32.697 --> 00:02:34.280
<i>(telephone ringing)</i>

00:02:34.971 --> 00:02:36.554
<i>(telephone ringing)</i>

00:02:37.259 --> 00:02:38.842
<i>(telephone ringing)</i>

00:02:39.543 --> 00:02:41.126
<i>(telephone ringing louder)</i>

00:02:41.843 --> 00:02:43.426
<i>(telephone ringing)</i>

00:02:44.102 --> 00:02:45.685
<i>(telephone ringing)</i>

00:02:46.416 --> 00:02:47.999
<i>(telephone ringing)</i>

00:02:48.205 --> 00:02:50.477
<i>(telephone ringing)</i>
<v Proog>Proog: You’re not paying attention!</v>

00:02:50.502 --> 00:02:54.319
<v Emo>Emo: (huffs) I—I just
want to answer the phone.</v>

00:02:54.685 --> 00:02:57.114
<v Proog>Proog: Emo, look— I mean listen.</v>

00:02:58.075 --> 00:02:59.896
<i>(slimy warbling)</i>

00:02:59.921 --> 00:03:01.819
<v Proog>You have to learn to listen.</v>

00:03:03.289 --> 00:03:05.187
<v Proog>This is not some game.</v>

00:03:05.212 --> 00:03:09.242
<v Proog>You, I mean we—
we could easily die out here.</v>

00:03:09.267 --> 00:03:11.075
<v Proog>(sighs) Listen.</v>

00:03:11.616 --> 00:03:13.881
<v Proog>Listen to the sounds of the machine.</v>

00:03:14.573 --> 00:03:15.573
<i>(clock ticking slowly)</i>

00:03:18.201 --> 00:03:19.646
<v Proog>Listen to your breathing.</v>

00:03:23.050 --> 00:03:25.150
<i>(blocks thudding, quiet
buzzing, clock still ticking)</i>

00:03:30.196 --> 00:03:32.939
<i>(buzzing getting louder)</i>

00:03:34.635 --> 00:03:37.135
<v Emo>Emo: (laughs)</v>

00:03:37.160 --> 00:03:38.482
<i>(key clicks)</i>

00:03:41.333 --> 00:03:43.966
<i>(slow, heavy footsteps)</i>

00:03:43.991 --> 00:03:46.104
<i>(sharp, metallic bang)</i>

00:03:46.129 --> 00:03:47.971
♪ (upbeat curious music)

00:03:49.451 --> 00:03:51.356
<i>(slimy bounce)</i>

00:03:53.240 --> 00:03:55.287
♪ (music intensifying)

00:03:58.648 --> 00:04:00.945
♪ (ominous music swells)

00:04:05.742 --> 00:04:07.813
<i>(loud metal thud)</i>

00:04:09.180 --> 00:04:10.429
<i>(metal snapping in place)</i>

00:04:10.454 --> 00:04:12.328
♪ (adventurous, tribal orchestration)

00:04:12.353 --> 00:04:13.651
<i>(metal clattering)</i>

00:04:13.676 --> 00:04:15.676 position:100% line:0%
♪

00:04:20.594 --> 00:04:21.594
<i>(loud metal clattering)</i>

00:04:26.960 --> 00:04:29.069
<v Emo>Emo: Well, don’t
you ever get tired of this?</v>

00:04:29.343 --> 00:04:31.177
<v Proog>Proog: Tired?!</v>
<v Emo>Emo: Yeah.</v>

00:04:31.407 --> 00:04:35.004
<v Proog>Proog: Emo, the
machine is like clockwork!</v>

00:04:35.361 --> 00:04:39.190
<v Proog>One move out of place
and you’re ground to a pulp.</v>

00:04:39.331 --> 00:04:40.331
<i>(loud metal thud)</i>

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:42.606
<i>(huge blast)</i>
<v Emo>Emo: But isn’t there the… like—</v>

00:04:42.631 --> 00:04:45.950
<v Proog>Proog: Pulp, Emo! Is
that what you want? Pulp?</v>

00:04:47.575 --> 00:04:49.957
<v Proog>Emo, your goal in life…</v>

00:04:50.732 --> 00:04:52.169
<v Proog>… pulp?!</v>

00:05:03.296 --> 00:05:05.851
<i>(elevator doors creak closed)</i>

00:05:06.769 --> 00:05:07.769
<v Proog>Proog: (presses button)</v>

00:05:07.794 --> 00:05:09.074
<i>(metallic clanging and whirring)</i>

00:05:09.099 --> 00:05:10.099
<i>(elevator caves in)</i>

00:05:10.124 --> 00:05:11.262
<i>(rusty whirring)</i>

00:05:12.200 --> 00:05:13.525
<i>(metal doors locking)</i>

00:05:18.130 --> 00:05:20.075
<i>(elevator rumbling)</i>

00:05:21.542 --> 00:05:23.575
<i>(metal scrapes)</i>

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:25.200
<i>(white noise intensifies)</i>

00:05:25.225 --> 00:05:26.650
<i>(floor crashes down)</i>

00:05:26.675 --> 00:05:27.835
<i>(metal clanging and whirring)</i>

00:05:27.860 --> 00:05:29.000
<i>(elevator rumbles)</i>

00:05:29.594 --> 00:05:31.875
<i>(mechanical arm whirring and hissing)</i>

00:05:32.430 --> 00:05:33.586
<i>(mechanical acceleration)</i>

00:05:33.719 --> 00:05:35.030
<i>(metal doors locking)</i>

00:05:41.492 --> 00:05:43.742
<v Proog>Proog: Emo, close your eyes.</v>

00:05:44.624 --> 00:05:45.824
<v Emo>Emo: Why?</v>
<v Proog>Proog: Now!</v>

00:05:51.405 --> 00:05:52.467
<v Emo>Emo: Okay…</v>

00:05:53.653 --> 00:05:54.653
<v Proog>Proog: Good.</v>

00:05:59.552 --> 00:06:01.851
<v Proog>What do you see at your left side, Emo?</v>

00:06:01.876 --> 00:06:02.876
<v Emo>Emo: Well…</v>

00:06:03.796 --> 00:06:05.686
<v Emo>… nothing.</v>
<v Proog>Proog: Really?</v>

00:06:06.499 --> 00:06:08.835
<v Emo>Emo: No, nothing at all.</v>
<v Proog>Proog: (quiet) Really?</v>

00:06:08.861 --> 00:06:12.077
<v Proog>Proog: And at your right, what
do you see at your right side, Emo?</v>

00:06:13.015 --> 00:06:15.492
<v Emo>Emo: (huffs) The same, Proog.</v>

00:06:15.517 --> 00:06:17.351
<v Emo>Exactly the same, nothing!</v>

00:06:17.376 --> 00:06:18.476
<i>(platform falls down)</i>

00:06:18.501 --> 00:06:19.501
<v Proog>Proog: Great.</v>

00:06:22.117 --> 00:06:23.849
<i>(platform accelerating down)</i>

00:06:23.874 --> 00:06:25.023
<i>(sharp metal bang)</i>

00:06:25.048 --> 00:06:26.048
<i>(camera shutter)</i>

00:06:27.320 --> 00:06:28.929
<i>(quiet camera shutters)</i>

00:06:36.531 --> 00:06:38.101
<i>(camera shutters getting louder)</i>

00:06:38.585 --> 00:06:40.512
<i>(portal warping and door slams)</i>

00:06:40.537 --> 00:06:42.920
<v Emo>Emo: Listen, Proog! Do you hear that?</v>

00:06:43.498 --> 00:06:44.693
<v Emo>Can we go here?</v>

00:06:45.396 --> 00:06:46.600
<v Proog>Proog: There?</v>
<v Emo>Emo: Yeah.</v>

00:06:46.625 --> 00:06:47.804
<v Proog>Proog: It isn’t safe, Emo.</v>

00:06:48.646 --> 00:06:49.770
<v Proog>Proog: (flicks device open)</v>

00:06:49.795 --> 00:06:52.301
<v Emo>Emo: But…</v>
<v Proog>Proog: Trust me, it’s not.</v>

00:06:53.219 --> 00:06:54.523
<v Emo>Emo: Or maybe I could—</v>

00:06:54.548 --> 00:06:56.398
<v Proog>Proog: No.</v>
<i>(static crackle)</i>

00:06:56.423 --> 00:06:58.078
<i>(camera shutter)</i>
<v Emo>Emo: But—</v>

00:06:58.102 --> 00:07:00.561
<v Proog>Proog: No! No!</v>

00:07:01.195 --> 00:07:03.530
<v Proog>Any further questions, Emo?</v>

00:07:04.359 --> 00:07:05.359
<v Emo>Emo: (quiet) No…</v>

00:07:07.819 --> 00:07:08.819
<i>(tile thuds)</i>

00:07:09.765 --> 00:07:11.390
<v Proog>Proog: Emo…</v>
<v Emo>Emo: Yeah?</v>

00:07:11.648 --> 00:07:13.273
<v Proog>Proog: Emo, why?</v>

00:07:13.562 --> 00:07:18.327
<v Proog>Emo, why can’t you
see the beauty of this place?</v>

00:07:18.984 --> 00:07:23.757
<v Proog>The way it works, how perfect it is.</v>

00:07:24.211 --> 00:07:27.074
<v Emo>Emo: No, Proog. I don’t see. </v>

00:07:27.098 --> 00:07:29.911
<v Emo>I don’t see because
there’s nothing there.</v>

00:07:31.351 --> 00:07:34.835
<v Emo>And why should I trust my
life to something that isn’t there?</v>

00:07:35.538 --> 00:07:36.913
<v Emo>Well, can you tell me that?</v>

00:07:36.938 --> 00:07:38.273
<v Proog>Proog: Emo…</v>
<v Emo>Emo: Answer me.</v>

00:07:40.819 --> 00:07:42.069
<v Proog>Proog: (slaps Emo)</v>

00:07:43.679 --> 00:07:44.870
<v Emo>Emo: Proog…</v>

00:07:44.894 --> 00:07:46.633
<v Emo>… you’re a sick man!</v>

00:07:46.658 --> 00:07:48.484 position:100% line:0%
♪ (intense chase music)

00:07:46.658 --> 00:07:48.484
<v Proog>Proog: Emo…</v>
<v Emo>Emo: Stay away from me!</v>

00:07:48.509 --> 00:07:49.509
<v Proog>Proog: Emo…</v>

00:07:50.414 --> 00:07:51.718
<i>(clock ticking)</i>

00:07:52.390 --> 00:07:54.804
<v Proog>Proog: No! Emo, it’s a trap!</v>

00:07:55.612 --> 00:07:57.354
<v Emo>Emo: Hah, “it’s a trap”!</v>

00:07:57.379 --> 00:08:01.603
<v Emo>At the left side, you can see
the Hanging Gardens of Babylon!</v>

00:08:01.628 --> 00:08:04.112
<i>(heavy rain‐like noise)</i>
<v Emo>How’s that for a trap?</v>

00:08:04.137 --> 00:08:05.764
<i>(bricks falling apart)</i>

00:08:05.789 --> 00:08:06.789
<v Proog>Proog: No, Emo!</v>

00:08:06.814 --> 00:08:09.338
<i>(structure collapses,
bricks clanging loudly)</i>

00:08:09.363 --> 00:08:12.793
<v Emo>Emo: And on the right side,
you can see— well guess what…</v>

00:08:12.818 --> 00:08:15.052
<v Emo>… the Colossus of Rhodes!</v>

00:08:15.489 --> 00:08:16.489
<v Proog>Proog: No!</v>

00:08:16.514 --> 00:08:17.766
<v Emo>Emo: The Colossus of Rhodes…</v>

00:08:17.790 --> 00:08:20.023
<v Emo>… and it is here just for you, Proog.</v>

00:08:20.062 --> 00:08:21.497
<v Emo>(laughs) “Just for you”.</v>

00:08:23.584 --> 00:08:24.884
<i>(sustained high‐frequency tone)</i>

00:08:25.633 --> 00:08:27.405
<i>(mechanical bellow)</i>

00:08:29.040 --> 00:08:30.407
<i>(deep roaring)</i>

00:08:32.026 --> 00:08:33.026
<v Proog>Proog: (thumps)</v>

00:08:41.843 --> 00:08:42.843
<v Proog>Proog: (swings snake)</v>

00:08:45.570 --> 00:08:46.640
<v Emo>Emo: (knocked over)</v>

00:08:51.163 --> 00:08:52.819
<v Proog>Proog: It is there.</v>

00:08:53.754 --> 00:08:56.316
<v Proog>I’m telling you, Emo.</v>

00:08:56.440 --> 00:08:59.439
<v Proog>(shuddering breath) It—it is. It is.</v>

00:09:02.333 --> 00:09:04.356
<i>(hollow icy ambience)</i>

00:09:05.785 --> 00:09:07.285
<i>(cold wind blowing softly)</i>

00:09:26.031 --> 00:09:28.101
<i>(hollow mechanical ambience)</i>

00:09:28.126 --> 00:09:29.694
♪ (melancholic orchestral music swells)
